item.title: Nomad 95: Rob Bell - Millones Cajones and How to Find Your True Self
item.description:
Nomad 95: Rob Bell - Millones Cajones and How to Find Your True Self

As if building a church of 10,000+, producing an international bestselling DVD series, writing critically acclaimed bestselling books, producing a hugely popular podcast, and having his own TV show wasn't enough, Rob Bell has decided to write a novel. And much to the frustration of all us lesser talented mortals, it's really rather good!
